\"jaspernationalpark\";i:35;s:10:\"processing\";i:36;s:6:\"clouds\";i:37;s:16:\"gargoylemountain\";i:38;s:5:\"light\";i:39;s:13:\"travelalberta\";i:40;s:5:\"peaks\";i:41;s:11:\"niksoftware\";i:42;s:10:\"photograph\";i:43;s:14:\"postprocessing\";i:44;s:6:\"travel\";i:45;s:7:\"digital\";i:46;s:9:\"photoshop\";i:47;s:5:\"adobe\";i:48;s:6:\"canada\";i:49;s:10:\"snowcapped\";i:50;s:12:\"northamerica\";i:51;s:5:\"nikon\";i:52;s:8:\"mountain\";}}i:1;a:25:{s:5:\"title\";s:8:\"Fortress\";s:3:\"url\";s:51:\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/thefella/44770212160/\";s:11:\"description\";s:1445:\"			<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\">TheFella</a> posted a photo:</p>\n	\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/thefella/44770212160/\" title=\"Fortress\"><img src=\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7856/44770212160_7f4af9bc76_m.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"160\" alt=\"Fortress\" /></a></p>\n\n<p>Fortress | Liepāja, Latvia <br />\n<a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/fortress\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/fortress</a> <br />\n <br />\nThe tide rises over an old Russian sea fortress off the coast of Liepāja in Latvia. Taken while on a shoot for the marvellous people at the Latvian tourist board.<br />\n<br />\nI haven\'t uploaded to Flickr in ages, but I\'m going to get back into it again. As a Smugmug ambassador, I was super happy when they took over my first photography website! Speaking of photography, I still have one space left on my <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/faroe-islands-may-2019\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">Faroe Islands photography workshop</a>, and I think two or three left on my <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/scotland-april-2019\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">Western Scotland workshop</a>.<br />\n <br />\nDetails <br />\nNikon D810 / ISO 40 / f/14 / 30s / Nikkor 14-24mm f/2.8G ED @ 14mm / Location: Liepāja, Latvia <br />\n <br />\nBuy a print: <br />\n<a href=\"https://thefella.smugmug.com/Galleries/All/i-ffxkkd8/buy\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">thefella.smugmug.com/Galleries/All/i-ffxkkd8/buy</a></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:1072:\"Fortress | Liepāja, Latvia \n<a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/fortress\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/fortress</a> \n \nThe tide rises over an old Russian sea fortress off the coast of Liepāja in Latvia. Taken while on a shoot for the marvellous people at the Latvian tourist board.\n\nI haven\'t uploaded to Flickr in ages, but I\'m going to get back into it again. As a Smugmug ambassador, I was super happy when they took over my first photography website! Speaking of photography, I still have one space left on my <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/faroe-islands-may-2019\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">Faroe Islands photography workshop</a>, and I think two or three left on my <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/scotland-april-2019\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">Western Scotland workshop</a>.\n \nDetails \nNikon D810 / ISO 40 / f/14 / 30s / Nikkor 14-24mm f/2.8G ED @ 14mm / Location: Liepāja, Latvia \n \nBuy a print: \n<a href=\"https://thefella.smugmug.com/Galleries/All/i-ffxkkd8/buy\" rel=\"noreferrer nofollow\">thefella.smugmug.com/Galleries/All/i-ffxkkd8/buy</a> \";s:5:\"m_url\";s:64:\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7856/44770212160_7f4af9bc76_m.jpg\";s:5:\"t_url\";s:64:\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7856/44770212160_7f4af9bc76_s.jpg\";s:5:\"l_url\";s:62:\"https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7856/44770212160_7f4af9bc76.jpg\";s:9:\"photo_xml\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"1546537188\";s:10:\"date_taken\";s:25:\"2017-08-18T10:57:50-08:00\";s:15:\"date_taken_nice\";s:17:\"August 18th, 2017\";s:4:\"guid\";s:18:\"/photo/44770212160\";s:11:\"author_name\";s:8:\"TheFella\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:39:\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\";s:11:\"author_nsid\";s:12:\"11224136@N07\";s:11:\"author_icon\";s:87:\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4239/buddyicons/11224136@N07.jpg?1498182937#11224136@N07\";s:9:\"photo_url\";s:64:\"https://farm8.staticfli