-islands-may-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">2017 workshop</a>, just after we hiked up to one of our favourite viewpoints. Everyone takes photos one direction. but I thought I\'d try the other way. I\'m off again to teach here in a few weeks (April). This one is sold out, but if you fancy coming on another workshop, <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/iceland-june-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">I\'ll be teaching in June in Iceland</a>.<br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>No images in comments please.</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>Details</b><br />\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 64 / f/8 / 1/200s / AF-S Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6G ED VR @ 28mm / Location: Eysturoy, Faroe Islands</i></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:1215:\"<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.500px.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">500px</a> | <a href=\"https://steller.co/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Steller</a></b>\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/after-the-storm\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/after-the-storm</a></b> \n\nLight on the mountains in the Faroe Islands just after a heavy storm. This was taken on my <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/faroe-islands-may-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">2017 workshop</a>, just after we hiked up to one of our favourite viewpoints. Everyone takes photos one direction. but I thought I\'d try the other way. I\'m off again to teach here in a few weeks (April). This one is sold out, but if you fancy coming on another workshop, <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/iceland-june-2018/\" rel=\"nofollow\">I\'ll be teaching in June in Iceland</a>.\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b>No images in comments please.</b>\n\n<b>Details</b>\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 64 / f/8 / 1/200s / AF-S Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6G ED VR @ 28mm / Location: Eysturoy, Faroe Islands</i>\";s:5:\"m_url\";s:64:\"http