s\";i:54;s:8:\"bluehour\";i:55;s:6:\"travel\";i:56;s:9:\"courtyard\";i:57;s:4:\"irix\";i:58;s:8:\"türkiye\";i:59;s:5:\"adobe\";i:60;s:8:\"thefella\";i:61;s:6:\"europe\";i:62;s:3:\"sky\";i:63;s:8:\"building\";}}i:7;a:25:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"Frozen Forest\";s:3:\"url\";s:51:\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/thefella/33906547140/\";s:11:\"description\";s:1911:\"			<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\">TheFella</a> posted a photo:</p>\n	\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/thefella/33906547140/\" title=\"Frozen Forest\"><img src=\"https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2838/33906547140_41c74c619d_m.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"135\" alt=\"Frozen Forest\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><b><a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://thefella.com/snapchat\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snapchat</a></b><br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/frozen-forest\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/frozen-forest</a></b> <br />\n<br />\nI\'ve not really been on Flickr much recently, but hopefully that hiatus is over! This is a frozen forest inside the Arctic Circle in the very north of Finland. I was on a shoot for Ford and decided to shoot the surrounding area as well. I didn\'t have to go far into this forest before I found a scene that pleased me!<br />\n<br />\nI\'m just back from shooting in Italy, so I\'ll try and get some portfolio shots from that up soon. I also have some Instagram shots up on <a href=\"https://instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">@thefella</a>. Off to Poland next week with <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/murphyzmike\">Murphyz</a> and <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/johnessl\">John</a>, then heading to the Faroe Islands to teach my <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/faroe-islands-may-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 workshop</a>. Busy few weeks ahead!<br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>No images in comments please.</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>Details</b><br />\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 160 / f/8 / 1/20s / AF-S Nikkor 50mm f/1.4G @ 50mm / Location: Arctic Circle, Finland</i></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:1503:\"<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://thefella.com/snapchat\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snapchat</a></b>\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/frozen-forest\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/frozen-forest</a></b> \n\nI\'ve not really been on Flickr much recently, but hopefully that hiatus is over! This is a frozen forest inside the Arctic Circle in the very north of Finland. I was on a shoot for Ford and decided to shoot the surrounding area as well. I didn\'t have to go far into this forest before I found a scene that pleased me!\n\nI\'m just back from shooting in Italy, so I\'ll try and get some portfolio shots from that up soon. I also have some Instagram shots up on <a href=\"https://instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">@thefella</a>. Off to Poland next week with <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/murphyzmike\">Murphyz</a> and <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/johnessl\">John</a>, then heading to the Faroe Islands to teach my <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/faroe-islands-may-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 workshop</a>. Busy few weeks ahead!\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b>No images in comments please.</b>\n\n<b>Details</b>\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 160 / f/8 / 1/20s / AF-S Nikkor 50mm f/1.4G @ 50mm / Location: Arctic Circle, Finland</i>\";s:5:\"m_url\";s:64:\"https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2838/3