:\"House of a Thousand Colours\";s:3:\"url\";s:51:\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/thefella/32749210945/\";s:11:\"description\";s:1531:\"			<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\">TheFella</a> posted a photo:</p>\n	\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/thefella/32749210945/\" title=\"House of a Thousand Colours\"><img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/412/32749210945_0e0bf53bd2_m.jpg\" width=\"159\" height=\"240\" alt=\"House of a Thousand Colours\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><b><a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Twitter</a></b><br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/house-of-a-thousand-colours\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/house-of-a-thousand-colours</a></b> <br />\n<br />\nThis is a place I\'ve been wanting to see for a while now! It\'s a colourful office block on Odaiba island in Tokyo. I went here when I was shooting in Japan for the <a href=\"http://www.gotokyo.org/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tokyo Tourist Board</a>.<br />\n<br />\nYou can see more of my photos from this amazing city on my website: <a href=\"https://thefella.com/commission/tokyo-tourism\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/tokyo</a>.<br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>No images in comments please.</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>Details</b><br />\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 400 / f/5 / 1/20s / AF-S Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6G ED VR @ 28mm / Location: Tokyo, Japan</i></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:1097:\"<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://twitter.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Twitter</a></b>\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/house-of-a-thousand-colours\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/house-of-a-thousand-colours</a></b> \n\nThis is a place I\'ve been wanting to see for a while now! It\'s a colourful office block on Odaiba island in Tokyo. I went here when I was shooting in Japan for the <a href=\"http://www.gotokyo.org/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tokyo Tourist Board</a>.\n\nYou can see more of my photos from this amazing city on my website: <a href=\"https://thefella.com/commission/tokyo-tourism\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/tokyo</a>.\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b>No images in comments please.</b>\n\n<b>Details</b>\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 400 / f/5 / 1/20s / AF-S Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6G ED VR @ 28mm / Location: Tokyo, Japan</i>\n\";s:5:\"m_url\";s:63:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/412/32749210945_0e0bf53bd2_m.jpg\";s:5:\"t_url\";s:63:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/412/32749210945_0e0bf53bd2_s.jpg\";s:5:\"l_url\";s:61:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/412/32749210945_0e0bf53bd2.jpg\";s:9:\"photo_xml\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"1486402168\";s:10:\"date_taken\";s:25:\"2017-01-13T07:41:01-08:00\";s:15:\"date_taken_nice\";s:18:\"January 13th, 2017\";s:4:\"guid\";s:18:\"/photo/32749210945\";s:11:\"author_name\";s:8:\"TheFella\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:39:\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\";s:11:\"author_nsid\";s:12:\"11224136@N07\";s:11:\"author_icon\";s:87:\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4239/buddyicons/11224136@N07.jpg?1498182937#11224136@N07\";s:9:\"photo_url\";s:63:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/412/32749210945_0e0bf53bd2_b.jpg\";s:9:\"thumb_url\";s:63:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/412/32749210945_0e0bf53bd2_s.jpg\";s:6:\"height\";s:4:\"1024\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"680\";s:7:\"l_width\";s:3:\"332\";s:4:\"tags\";s:607:\"東京府 colours asia slr お台場 千色の家 floors tokyotourism thesoho 