<a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://thefella.com/snapchat\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snapchat</a></b><br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/solitary-saksun\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/solitary-saksun</a></b> <br />\n<br />\nI\'ve just released tickets for my landscape photography workshop in the Faroe Islands! It\'ll take place on <b>13-20 May, 2017</b>. There are 10 spaces, although as of writing this, we only have <b>3 spaces left</b>! <br />\n<br />\nIf you\'re interested, head to <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/faroe-islands-may-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">f8workshops.com</a> to find out more information and secure your spot. This is genuinely selling out really fast.<br />\n<br />\nThis photos is of a lone turf-roofed house stands surrounded by mountains in the village of Saksun, one of the locations I\'ll be taking you to!<br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>No images in comments please.</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>Details</b><br />\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 64 / f/8 / 1/1250s / AF-S Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6G ED VR @ 28mm / Location: Saksun, Faroe Islands</i></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:1260:\"<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://thefella.com/snapchat\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snapchat</a></b>\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/solitary-saksun\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/solitary-saksun</a></b> \n\nI\'ve just released tickets for my landscape photography workshop in the Faroe Islands! It\'ll take place on <b>13-20 May, 2017</b>. There are 10 spaces, although as of writing this, we only have <b>3 spaces left</b>! \n\nIf you\'re interested, head to <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/faroe-islands-may-2017/\" rel=\"nofollow\">f8workshops.com</a> to find out more information and secure your spot. This is genuinely selling out really fast.\n\nThis photos is of a lone turf-roofed house stands surrounded by mountains in the village of Saksun, one of the locations I\'ll be taking you to!\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b>No images in comments please.</b>\n\n<b>Details</b>\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 64 / f/8 / 1/1250s / AF-S Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6G ED VR @ 28mm / Location: Saksun, Faroe Islands</i>\n\";s:5:\"m_url\";s:63:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/287/32612596966_8202896858_m.jpg\";s:5:\"t_url\";s:63:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/287/32612596966_8202896858_s.jpg\";s:5:\"l_url\";s:61:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/287/32612596966_8202896858.jpg\";s:9:\"photo_xml\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"1485980896\";s:10:\"date_taken\";s:25:\"2016-05-24T12:06:01-08:00\";s:15:\"date_taken_nice\";s:14:\"May 24th, 2016\";s:4:\"guid\";s:18:\"/photo/32612596966\";s:11:\"author_name\";s:8:\"TheFella\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:39:\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\";s:11:\"author_nsid\";s:12:\"11224136@N07\";s:11:\"author_icon\";s:87:\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4239/buddyicons/11224136@N07.jpg?1498182937#11224136@N07\";s:9:\"photo_url\";s:63:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/287/32612596966_8202896858_b.jpg\";s:9:\"thumb_url\";s:63:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/287/32612596966_8202896858_s.jpg\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"683\";s:5:\"width\";s:4:\"1024\";s:7:\"l_width\";s:3:\"500\";s:4:\"tags\";s:421:\"grass rock hut slr water turf lake faroearchipelago beach ocean thefellaphotography coastal conormacneill thefella photograph d810 visitfaroeislands travelphotography kingdomofdenmark inlet faroese sky nikon sea saksun grassroof roof mountains streymoy processing postprocessing photography waves fjord photo atlanticocean saksunar lagoon travel faroeislands house sundakommuna faroes dslr digital coast atlantic mountain\";s:5:\"tagsa\";a:48:{i:0;s:5:\"grass\";i:1;s:4:\"rock\";i:2;s:3:\"hut\";i:3;s:3:\"slr\";i:4;s:5:\"water\";i:5;s:4:\"turf\";i:6;s:4:\"lake\";i:7;s:16:\"faroearchipelago\";i:8;s:5:\"beach\";i:9;s:5:\"ocean\";i:10;s:19:\"thefellaphotography\";i:11;s:7:\"coastal\";i:12;s:13:\"conormacneill\";i:13;s:8:\"thefella\";i:14;s:10:\"photograph\";i:15;s:4:\"d810\";i:16;s:17:\"visitfaroeislands\";i:17;s:17:\"travelphotography\";i:18;s:16:\"kingdomofdenmark\";i:19;s:5:\"inlet\";i:20;s:7:\"faroese\";i:21;s:3:\"sky\";i:22;s:5:\"nikon\";i:23;s:3:\"sea\";i:24;s:6:\"saksun\";i:25;s:9:\"grassroof\";i:26;s:4:\"roof\";i:27;s:9:\"mountains\";i:28;s:8:\"streymoy\";i:29;s:10:\"processing\";i:30;s:14:\"postprocessing\";i:31;s:11:\"photography\";i:32;s:5:\"waves\";i:33;s:5:\"fjord\";i:34;s:5:\"photo\";i:35;s:13:\"atlanticocean\";i:36;s:8:\"saksunar\";i:37;s:6:\"lagoon\";i:38;s:6:\"travel\";i:39;s:12:\"faroeislands\";i:40;s:5:\"house\";i:41;s:12:\"sundakommuna\";i:42;s:6:\"faroes\";i:43;s:4:\"dslr\";i:44;s:7:\"digital\";i:45;s:5:\"coast\";i:46;s:8:\"atlantic\";i:47;s:8:\"mountain\";}s:10:\"photo_mime\";s:10:\"image/jpeg\";s:9:\"tags_list\";a:48:{i:0;s:5:\"grass\";i:1;s:4:\"rock\";i:2;s:3:\"hut\";i:3;s:3:\"slr\";i:4;s:5:\"water\";i:5;s:4:\"turf\";i:6;s:4:\"lake\";i:7;s:16:\"faroearchipelago\";i:8;s:5:\"beach\";i:9;s:5:\"ocean\";i:10;s:19:\"thefellaphotography\";i:11;s:7:\"coastal\";i:12;s:13:\"conormacneill\";i:13;s:8:\"thefella\";i:14;s:10:\"photograph\";i:15;s:4:\"d810\";i:16;s:17:\"visitfaroeislands\";i:17;s:17:\"travelphotography\";i:18;s:16:\"kingdomofdenmark\";i:19;s:5:\"inlet\";i:20;s:7:\"faroese\";i:21;s:3:\"sky\";i:22;s:5:\"nikon\";i:23;s:3:\"sea\";i:24;s:6:\"saksun\";i:25;s:9:\"grassroof\";i:26;s:4:\"roof\";i:27;s:9:\"mountains\";i:28;s:8:\"streymoy\";i:29;s:10:\"processing\";i:30;s:14:\"postprocessing\";i:31;s:11:\"photography\";i:32;s:5:\"waves\";i:33;s:5:\"fjord\";i:34;s:5:\"photo\";i:35;s:13:\"atlanticocean\";i:36;s:8:\"saksunar\";i:37;s:6:\"lagoon\";i:38;s:6:\"travel\";i:39;s:12:\"faroeislands\";i:40;s:5:\"house\";i:41;s:12:\"sundakommuna\";i:42;s:6:\"faroes\";i:43;s:4:\"dslr\";i:44;s:7:\"digital\";i:45;s:5:\"coast\";i:46;s:8:\"atlantic\";i:47;s:8:\"mountain\";}}i:10;a:25:{s:5:\"title\";s:6:\"Glenoe\";s:3:\"url\";s:51:\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/thefella/29406972965/\";s:11:\"description\";s:1731:\"			<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\">TheFella</a> posted a photo:</p>\n	\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/thefella/29406972965/\" title=\"Glenoe\"><img src=\"https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8540/29406972965_31ba8c133b_m.jpg\" width=\"166\" height=\"240\" alt=\"Glenoe\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><b><a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://thefella.com/snapchat\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snapchat</a></b><br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/glenoe\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/glenoe</a></b> <br />\n<br />\nA few weeks ago, I went back to Belfast, Northern Ireland, to see my friends and family (and for a shoot for Guardian Travel). One day, I decided to research some locations and I found out about this waterfall about 30 mins drive from my house. No-one I talked to had really heard of it! Well, here is Glenoe Waterfall, between Larne and Carrickfergus.<br />\n<br />\nIt was sunny, but raining and I couldn\'t get the composition I wanted from the edge, so I rolled up my jeans, took off my shoes and socks and waded through the river for about an hour. It was pretty cold and painful, and I kept getting splashes of water on the lens from being so low to the river, but I think it was worth it.<br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>No images in comments please.</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>Details</b><br />\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 160 / f/22 / 1/6s / Nikkor 14-24mm f/2.8G ED @ 24mm / Location: Country Antrim, United Kingdom</i></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:1338:\"<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://thefella.com/snapchat\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snapchat</a></b>\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/glenoe\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/glenoe</a></b> \n\nA few weeks ago, I went back to Belfast, Northern Ireland, to see my friends and family (and for a shoot for Guardian Travel). One day, I decided to research some locations and I found out about this waterfall about 30 mins drive from my house. No-one I talked to had really heard of it! Well, here is Glenoe Waterfall, between Larne and Carrickfergus.\n\nIt was sunny, but raining and I couldn\'t get the composition I wanted from the edge, so I rolled up my jeans, took off my shoes and socks and waded through the river for about an hour. It was pretty cold and painful, and I kept getting splashes of water on the lens from being so low to the river, but I think it was worth it.\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b>No images in comments please.</b>\n\n<b>Details</b>\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 160 / f/22 / 1/6s / Nikkor 14-24mm f/2.8G ED @ 24mm / Location: Country Antrim, United Kingdom</i>\n\";s:5:\"m_url\";s:64:\"https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8540/29406972965_31ba8c133b_m.jpg\";s:5:\"t_url\";s:64:\"https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8540/29406972965_31ba8c133b_s.jpg\";s:5:\"l_url\";s:62:\"https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8540/29406972965_31ba8c133b.jpg\";s:9:\"photo_xml\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"1472831035\";s:10: