l</a></b> <br />\n<br />\nMy <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/faroe-islands-may-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Faroe Island Workshop</a> next month is sold out, but you can still visit the site and join our mailing list to get first chance at our other ones! I have a few exciting trips coming up, so follow me on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> and <a href=\"https://thefella.com/snapchat\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snapchat</a>.<br />\n<br />\nThis photo is Solna Centrum station on the blue line (T11) of the Stockholm metro system in Sweden.<br />\n<br />\nYou can see more of my photos from Stockholm on <a href=\"http://www.boredpanda.com/stockholm-metro-art-conor-macneill/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Bored Panda</a>.<br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>No images in comments please.</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>Details</b><br />\n<i>Nikon D810 / ISO 31 / f/16 / 5s / Nikkor 14-24mm f/2.8G ED @ 14mm / Location: Stockholm, Sweden</i></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:1330:\"<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a> | <a href=\"https://thefella.com/snapchat\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snapchat</a></b>\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/secret-hell\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/secret-hell</a></b> \n\nMy <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/faroe-islands-may-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Faroe Island Workshop</a> next month is sold out, but you can still visit the site and join our mailing list to get first chance at our other ones! I have a few exciting trips coming up, so follow me on <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> and <a href=\"https://thefella.com/snapchat\" rel=\"nofollow\">Snapchat</a>.\n\nThis photo is Solna Centrum station on 