obe\";i:27;s:12:\"trainstation\";i:28;s:10:\"processing\";i:29;s:4:\"cave\";i:30;s:6:\"nordic\";i:31;s:7:\"sverige\";i:32;s:10:\"escalators\";i:33;s:4:\"dslr\";i:34;s:11:\"scandinavia\";i:35;s:7:\"exposed\";i:36;s:5:\"solna\";i:37;s:12:\"scandinavian\";i:38;s:12:\"metrostation\";i:39;s:7:\"bedrock\";i:40;s:9:\"lightroom\";i:41;s:10:\"tunnelbana\";i:42;s:5:\"tbana\";i:43;s:7:\"cadmium\";i:44;s:14:\"postprocessing\";i:45;s:17:\"travelphotography\";i:46;s:8:\"bloodred\";i:47;s:15:\"kingdomofsweden\";i:48;s:4:\"d810\";i:49;s:12:\"solnacentrum\";i:50;s:20:\"stockholmstunnelbana\";i:51;s:8:\"thefella\";i:52;s:13:\"conormacneill\";i:53;s:12:\"andersåberg\";i:54;s:19:\"thefellaphotography\";i:55;s:13:\"karlolavbjork\";i:56;s:7:\"t11line\";i:57;s:11:\"cadminumred\";i:58;s:26:\"theworldslongestartgallery\";}}i:13;a:25:{s:5:\"title\";s:10:\"Gásadalur\";s:3:\"url\";s:51:\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/thefella/24954552881/\";s:11:\"description\";s:1988:\"			<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\">TheFella</a> posted a photo:</p>\n	\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/thefella/24954552881/\" title=\"Gásadalur\"><img src=\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1670/24954552881_413ff1365f_m.jpg\" width=\"192\" height=\"240\" alt=\"Gásadalur\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><b><a href=\"http://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"http://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Photo Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a></b><br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/gasadalur\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/gasadalur</a></b> <br />\n<br />\nDelighted to announce my first landscape photography workshop in the Faroe Islands, taking place from May 14-21!<br />\n<br />\nI’ll be teaching alongside <a href=\"http://gregannandale.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Greg Annandale</a> and <a href=\"http://danrubin.is\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dan Rubin</a> with all the difficult behind the scenes work being handled by our producer, the wonderful <a href=\"http://www.zoetimmers.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Zoe Timmers</a>.<br />\n<br />\nCheck the link in my profile or head straight to <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/faroe-islands-may-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">f8workshops.com</a> and try and get one of our early bird tickets! (£100 off)<br />\n<br />\nThis workshop is in association with <a href=\"http://www.visitfaroeislands.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Visit Faroe Islands</a>, so you’re in for a treat!<br />\n<br />\nWith only 10 spaces in total and a few already sold to people interested in our last Iceland workshop, you’d better hurry! This is a photography adventure not to be missed! <br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>No images in comments please.</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>Details</b><br />\n<i>Nikon D800 / ISO 200 / f/8 / 21s / Nikkor 14-24mm f/2.8G ED @ 17mm / Location: Gásadalur, Faroe Islands</i></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:1550:\"<b><a href=\"http://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"http://f8workshops.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Photo Workshops</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a></b>\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/gasadalur\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/gasadalur</a></b> \n\nDelighted to announce my first landscape photography workshop in the Faroe Islands, taking place from May 14-21!\n\nI’ll be teaching alongside <a href=\"http://gregannandale.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Greg Annandale</a> and <a href=\"http://danrubin.is\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dan Rubin</a> with all the difficult behind the scenes work being handled by our producer, the wonderful <a href=\"http://www.zoetimmers.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Zoe Timmers</a>.\n\nCheck the link in my profile or head straight to <a href=\"https://f8workshops.com/faroe-islands-may-2016/\" rel=\"nofollow\">f8workshops.com</a> and try and get one of our early bird tickets! (£100 off)\n\nThis workshop is in association with <a href=\"http://www.visitfaroeislands.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Visit Faroe Islands</a>, so you’re in for a treat!\n\nWith only 10 spaces in total and a few already sold to people interested in our last Iceland workshop, you’d better hurry! This is a photography adventure not to be missed! \n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b>No images in comments please.</b>\n\n<b>Details</b>\n<i>Nikon D800 / ISO 200 / f/8 / 21s / Nikkor 14-24mm f/2.8G ED @ 17mm / Location: Gásadalur, Faroe Islands</i>\";s:5:\"m_url\";s:64:\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1670/24954552881_413ff1365f_m.jpg\";s:5:\"t_url\";s:64:\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1670/24954552881_413ff1365f_s.jpg\";s:5:\"l_url\";s:62:\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1670/24954552881_413ff1365f.jpg\";s:9:\"photo_xml\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"1455555949\";s:10:\"date_taken\";s:25:\"2015-08-01T05:26:55-08:00\";s:15:\"date_taken_nice\";s:16:\"August 1st, 2015\";s:4:\"guid\";s:18:\"/photo/24954552881\";s:11:\"author_name\";s:8:\"TheFella\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:39:\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\";s:11:\"author_nsid\";s:12:\"11224136@N07\";s:11:\"author_icon\";s:87:\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4239/buddyicons/11224136@N07.jpg?1498182937#11224136@N07\";s:9:\"photo_url\";s:64:\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1670/24954552881_413ff1365f_b.jpg\";s:9:\"thumb_url\";s:64:\"https://farm2.staticflickr.com/1670/24954552881_413ff1365f_s.jpg\";s:6:\"height\";s:4:\"1024\";s:5:\"width\";s:3:\"819\";s:7:\"l_width\";s:3:\"400\";s:4:\"tags\";s:598:\"ocean longexposure travel houses sea sky cliff mountain slr water grass clouds digital photoshop sunrise buildings landscape denmark photography islands photo waterfall nikon rocks europe european village cloudy rocky cliffs photograph adobe le danish strata processing nordic dslr atlanticocean faroeislands scandinavi