\";i:58;s:18:\"saganobambooforest\";i:59;s:13:\"conormacneill\";i:60;s:14:\"kyotoosakakobe\";i:61;s:19:\"thefellaphotography\";}}i:16;a:25:{s:5:\"title\";s:9:\"The Andes\";s:3:\"url\";s:51:\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/thefella/21598358374/\";s:11:\"description\";s:1315:\"			<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\">TheFella</a> posted a photo:</p>\n	\n<p><a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/thefella/21598358374/\" title=\"The Andes\"><img src=\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/718/21598358374_2bce9e3774_m.jpg\" width=\"240\" height=\"160\" alt=\"The Andes\" /></a></p>\n\n<p><b><a href=\"http://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"http://f8.pe\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Photo Expeditions</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a></b><br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/the-andes\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/the-andes</a></b> <br />\n<br />\nThis is possibly my favourite photo from my recent (and last-minute) trip to Ecuador for the Ministry of Tourism as part of their Feel Again Project. This particular shot was taken at the amazing Hacienda Zuleta in the Andes.<br />\n<br />\nSorry I haven\'t been as active on Flickr as usual; I didn\'t have much internet access over the last month or two.<br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>No images in comments please.</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>Details</b><br />\n<i>Nikon D800 / ISO 2000 / f/2.8 / 25s / Nikkor 14-24mm f/2.8G ED @ 16mm / Location: Cayambe, Ecuador</i></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:916:\"<b><a href=\"http://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"http://f8.pe\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Photo Expeditions</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a></b>\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/the-andes\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/the-andes</a></b> \n\nThis is possibly my favourite photo from my recent (and last-minute) trip to Ecuador for the Ministry of Tourism as part of their Feel Again Project. This particular shot was taken at the amazing Hacienda Zuleta in the Andes.\n\nSorry I haven\'t been as active on Flickr as usual; I didn\'t have much internet access over the last month or two.\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b>No images in comments please.</b>\n\n<b>Details</b>\n<i>Nikon D800 / ISO 2000 / f/2.8 / 25s / Nikkor 14-24mm f/2.8G ED @ 16mm / Location: Cayambe, Ecuador</i>\";s:5:\"m_url\";s:63:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/718/21598358374_2bce9e3774_m.jpg\";s:5:\"t_url\";s:63:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/718/21598358374_2bce9e3774_s.jpg\";s:5:\"l_url\";s:61:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/718/21598358374_2bce9e3774.jpg\";s:9:\"photo_xml\";s:0:\"\";s:4:\"date\";s:10:\"1445007175\";s:10:\"date_taken\";s:25:\"2015-09-28T02:54:53-08:00\";s:15:\"date_taken_nice\";s:20:\"September 28th, 2015\";s:4:\"guid\";s:18:\"/photo/21598358374\";s:11:\"author_name\";s:8:\"TheFella\";s:10:\"author_url\";s:39:\"https://www.flickr.com/people/thefella/\";s:11:\"author_nsid\";s:12:\"11224136@N07\";s:11:\"author_icon\";s:87:\"https://farm5.staticflickr.com/4239/buddyicons/11224136@N07.jpg?1498182937#11224136@N07\";s:9:\"photo_url\";s:63:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/718/21598358374_2bce9e3774_b.jpg\";s:9:\"thumb_url\";s:63:\"https://farm1.staticflickr.com/718/21598358374_2bce9e3774_s.jpg\";s:6:\"height\";s:3:\"683\";s:5:\"width\";s:4:\"1024\";s:7:\"l_width\";s:3:\"500\";s:4:\"tags\";s:614:\"travel trees sky mountain mountains building tree slr southamerica nature field night clouds digital photoshop stars landscape photography star photo highlands ecuador nikon cloudy path farm astro sierra nighttime photograph adobe american astrophotography processing andes fields nightsky dslr americas constellation equator hacienda andea