book.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a></b><br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/the-lost-forest\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/the-lost-forest</a></b> <br />\n<br />\nAnother shot from The States, but this time from a couple of years ago. These trees are reflected in the Lost Lake in Mount Hood National Forest, Oregon. This trip was again with <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/daves-f-stop/\">Dave Morrow</a> and this time included <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/greg-a/\">Greg Annandale</a>.<br />\n<br />\nKeep up to date with my trips on <a href=\"https://instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">my Instagram: @thefella</a>.<br />\n<br />\n<b>-------</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>No images in comments please.</b><br />\n<br />\n<b>Details</b><br />\n<i>Nikon D800 / ISO 50 / f/16 / 1s / AF-S Nikkor 28-300mm f/3.5-5.6G ED VR @ 78mm / Location: Lost Lake, United States</i></p>\";s:15:\"description_raw\";s:1064:\"<b><a href=\"http://thefella.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">TheFella</a> | <a href=\"http://f8.pe\" rel=\"nofollow\">f/8 Photo Expeditions</a> | <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Instagram</a> | <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook</a></b>\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b><a href=\"https://thefella.com/photo/the-lost-forest\" rel=\"nofollow\">thefella.com/photo/the-lost-forest</a></b> \n\nAnother shot from The States, but this time from a couple of years ago. These trees are reflected in the Lost Lake in Mount Hood National Forest, Oregon. This trip was again with <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/daves-f-stop/\">Dave Morrow</a> and this time included <a href=\"https://www.flickr.com/photos/greg-a/\">Greg Annandale</a>.\n\nKeep up to date with my trips on <a href=\"https://instagram.com/thefella\" rel=\"nofollow\">my Instagram: @thefella</a>.\n\n<b>-------</b>\n\n<b>No images in comments please.</b>\n\n<b>Details</b>\n<i>Nikon D800 / ISO 